      <title>美国要求卢旺达停止干扰刚果东部的 GPS 信号</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/us-demands-rwanda-stop-jamming-gps-signal-in-war-torn-east-congo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务院要求卢旺达停止在刚果民主共和国东部使用 GPS 干扰设备，该地区数百万因冲突而流离失所的人民急需援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/us-demands-rwanda-stop-jamming-gps-signal-in-war-torn-east-congo</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 05:57:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普连任前美国敲定向 Rivian 和 Plug Power 投资数十亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/us-to-finalize-billions-in-funding-for-rivian-plug-before-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在当选总统唐纳德·特朗普返回白宫的几天前，拜登政府敲定了向电动汽车制造商 Rivian Automotive Inc. 和氢能公司 Plug Power Inc. 提供数十亿美元的融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/us-to-finalize-billions-in-funding-for-rivian-plug-before-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 02:17:27 GMT</pubDate>
